Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: pydemon
Version: 0.1.1
Summary: Monitor for any changes in your Project
Home-page: https://github.com/becxer/pydemon
Author: becxer
Author-email: becxer87@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: 
        ##How to install
         
        		$ sudo pip install pydemon
        
        ##How to use
        
        		$ pydemon 'bash script'
        		or
        		$ pydemon script.sh
        
        ##How to ignore file such as ".swp"
        
        		$ vi .pydemon.dat
        		
        		add your ignore pattern to "ignore_postfix" like below
        		
        		{
        			"ignore_postfix": [
        				".swp", 
        				".log"
        			],
        			"run_count": 16
        		}
        
        
